                     move  "DO  "         to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      rr-tip-cnv           to   v-num                  .
           perform   exe-acc-cmp-000      thru exe-acc-cmp-999        .
